org.embulk

Class EmbulkRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.embulk.EmbulkRunner

  • public class EmbulkRunner
extends java.lang.Object
    EmbulkRunner runs the guess, preview, or run subcommand. NOTE: Developers should not depend on this EmbulkRunner class. This class is created tentatively, and may be re-implemented again in a different style.
